    "title": "CarDekho is Hiring: E-commerce Executive (Junior)",
    "description": "CarDekho invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of E-commerce Executive at our Faridabad location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout CarDekho:\nCarDekho is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in Affiliate Marketing\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n• Proficiency in Content Writing\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Faridabad, Haryana, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with CarDekho!",
